== 工作室之旅 ==
[[File:Potter's_cottage,_Godric's_Hollow.jpg|右]]
伦敦华纳兄弟工作室之旅─哈利·波特的制作是在[[英格兰|英格兰]]东南部的{{link-en|利维斯登|Leavesden, Hertfordshire}}的一个公共景点。这是一个关于[[哈利波特系列電影|哈利·波特系列电影]]的幕后工作的永久性展览。

工作室之旅于2012年初向公众开放。许多哈利·波特系列电影的演职人员参加了盛大的开幕式。<ref>[http://www.snitchseeker.com/harry-potter-news/cast-list-revealed-for-harry-potter-leavesden-tour-grand-opening-88860/Cast List revealed for Warner Bros.]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.snitchseeker.com/harry-potter-news/cast-and-crew-attend-warner-bros-studio-tour-the-making-of-harry-potter-grand-opening-88915/ |title="Cast and Crew attends Warner Bros. |accessdate=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2016-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160925133202/http://www.snitchseeker.com/harry-potter-news/cast-and-crew-attend-warner-bros-studio-tour-the-making-of-harry-potter-grand-opening-88915/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

每次游览通常需要三个小时，<ref name="Mail">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2114972/Harry-Potter-studio-tour-review-See-inside-movie-sets-Leavesden.html|title=The magic of Harry Potter: See inside the studios where the movies were filmed (and the biggest disappearing act will be £100 for a family ticket and a wand)|last=Thomas|first=Liz|date=2012-03-14|publisher=''[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]''|accessdate=2012-07-25|location=London|archive-date=2012-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120729111735/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2114972/Harry-Potter-studio-tour-review-See-inside-movie-sets-Leavesden.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 工作室之旅每天能够接待6000游客。<ref name="Guardian Sabbagh">{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2012/jun/10/josh-berger-warner-bros-interview|title=Josh Berger on Leavesden film studios: Harry Potter's new chamber of secrets|last=Sabbagh|first=Dan|date=2012-06-10|publisher=''[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]''|accessdate=2012-07-25|location=London|archive-date=2012-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120706183243/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2012/jun/10/josh-berger-warner-bros-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>尽管制作哈利·波特的工作室属于华纳兄弟，但工作室之旅并不是一个主题公园，这是由于华纳兄弟已将许可出售给[[环球影业|环球影业]]。<ref name="Guardian Sabbagh"/>

虽然标准游览是自助式的，但这里也提供额外收费的各种导游服务。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A2Lm99KEu6U|title=''Warner Bros. Studio Tour London'''s accessibility guide to the tour|accessdate=2016-12-05|archive-date=2016-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007124248/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A2Lm99KEu6U|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 创作 ===
游览的布局和整体演示是由[[伯班克_(加利福尼亚州)|伯班克]]的{{link-en|鑫科威尔集团|Thinkwell Group}}与华纳兄弟以及电影制作人，包括[[美术指导|美术指导]]{{link-en|斯图尔特·克雷格|Stuart Craig}}，{{link-en|服装师|Set dresser}}{{link-en|斯蒂芬妮·麦克米兰|Stephenie McMillan}}，生物设计师{{link-en|尼克·杜德曼|Nick Dudman}}和{{link-en|特效总监|Special effects supervisor}}{{link-en|约翰·理查森|John Richardson (special effects designer)}}密切合作设计。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://thinkwellgroup.com/projects/the-making-of-harry-potter/ |title=Warner Bros. Studio Tour London: The Making of Harry Potter {{!}} Thinkwell Group {{!}} Experience Design CompanyThinkwell Group, Inc<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2016-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121220701/http://thinkwellgroup.com/projects/the-making-of-harry-potter/ |archive-date=2016-11-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 它只包括为哈利·波特系列电影实际创作或在制作中使用的设施、道具和服装。设施比如礼堂、邓布利多的办公室、[[哈利·波特中的地点#对角巷|对角巷]]、[[魔法部|魔法部]]、格兰芬多公共房间和男生宿舍、海格的小屋以及1:24比例模型的[[霍格沃茨魔法学校|霍格沃茨]]城堡。
