=== 扩建 ===
华纳兄弟持续的在学校假期时推出特别专题，如黑魔法和动物演员。一些像挥舞魔杖互动和女贞路4号外景内部之类的设施都非常受欢迎，它们在各自的专题关闭后仍然得以保留。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wbstudiotour.co.uk/the-tour-experience/whats-on|title=Warner's list of upcoming special features at the tour|author=Warner Bros.|accessdate=2016-12-05|archive-date=2016-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161212234844/https://www.wbstudiotour.co.uk/the-tour-experience/whats-on|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年1月，工作室之旅发布首次扩建─一个新的9¾站台单元，游客能够登上在电影中使用的[[霍格沃茨特快列车|霍格沃茨特快列车]]的蒸汽机车头后面的原始车厢。设施包括在电影中出现的{{link-en|英国第5972号沃尔顿豪华列车|GWR 4900 Class 5972 Olton Hall}}（车上标示5972号霍格沃茨城堡）和{{link-en|英国铁路1号|British Railways Mark 1}}火车，均由{{link-en|约翰·理查森|John Richardson (special effects designer)}}的特效团队提供。最后还有一个新的绿幕体验，演示从演员的角度来看电影是如何拍摄的。这一部分于2015年3月底推出。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a624178/harry-potter-studio-tour-announces-new-permanent-platform-9--section.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-12-05 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924125146/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a624178/harry-potter-studio-tour-announces-new-permanent-platform-9--section.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在{{link-en|伯班克华纳兄弟制片厂|Warner Bros. Studios, Burbank}}的游览已改名为{{link-en|好莱坞华纳兄弟工作室之旅|Warner Bros. Studio Tour Hollywood}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wbstudiotour.com/|title=Official site of Warner Bros. Studio Tour Hollywood|author=Warner Bros.|accessdate=2016-12-05|archive-date=2016-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203091255/https://www.wbstudiotour.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>（之前被称为华纳兄弟工作室VIP之旅）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aaa.com/travelinfo/california/los-angeles/attractions/the-warner-bros-studios-vip-tour-504378.html|title=aaa archival info on 'warner bros. studios VIP tour|author=aaa.com|accessdate=2016-12-05|archive-date=2017-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122054345/http://www.aaa.com/travelinfo/california/los-angeles/attractions/the-warner-bros-studios-vip-tour-504378.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.seeing-stars.com/StudioTours/WarnerBrosTour.shtml|title=seeing-stars.com's archival info on 'warner bros. studios VIP tour|author=seeing-stars.com|accessdate=2016-12-05|archive-date=2016-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160714223624/http://www.seeing-stars.com/StudioTours/WarnerBrosTour.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> 华纳对游览进行了改造，为游客提供更多的设施和选择。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.eventmagazine.co.uk/warner-bros-studio-tour-london-making-harry-potter/venues/article/1392934|title=the Warner Bros. Studio Tour London venue is also available to hire for private events|author=eventmagazine.co.uk|accessdate=2016-12-05|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816234527/http://www.eventmagazine.co.uk/warner-bros-studio-tour-london-making-harry-potter/venues/article/1392934|dead-url=no}}</ref>

